cs.FL, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.DM, cs.CC

Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a subclass of automata for data languages.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper discusses the recognition power of the automata in terms of logical expressiveness.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) are possible categories as the paper deals with data languages and their recognition by automata.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the decidability of the emptiness problem for the automata.
